					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yeah, calling the main thread &quot;reset&quot; can be a bit confusing, I wouldn't normally do that, but that's what the post I was replying to called it, and I didn't want to make things more confusing by changing the terminology.<br /><br />The main thread does indeed start at the reset vector, but any game that's not trivially simple will not have any game loops particularly close to the reset code.</div>

