						<div class="postbody">I did several smallish assembly programs for some small microcontrollers, and the main loop was right below the &quot;Reset&quot; label, so I named the main thread simply &quot;reset&quot;; the documentation would say, &quot;[this subroutine] must be called from reset&quot; instead of &quot;(...) from main thread&quot;.</div>

