					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p186980">Re: Reset handler/reset vector confusion?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=186980&amp;sid=3596e59f603a7364cfb2cc1acc469386#p186980"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Wed Jan 18, 2017 4:13 am&nbsp;</div></td>
